veteran journalist and author sandra mackey died sunday , her son , colin mackey , said .
she was 77 .
her extensive career began in anonymity .
she was an undercover reporter working for u.s. newspapers from saudi arabia as her husband , dr. dan mackey , worked in a riyadh hospital .
for four years , she hid her writing from the authorities and smuggled her stories out of the country to get around saudi arabia 's prohibition on foreign journalists .
her work appeared under the pseudonym michael collins .